snippet.title: Jacob Jazz´s Marley & Marley Trailer
snippet.description:
Happy to announce my 2021xmas horror short game!

MARLEY & MARLEY

Horrifying adaptation of Charles Dickens "A Christmas Carol"

Ebenezer Srooge on christmas eve when ghosts attacked him

BAH! HAMBUG!

Part of the game Tamarindos Freaking Dinner, created by Jacob Jazz under the Celery Emblem label. published by Neon Doctrine 2021.
